 <body region="横下" xml:space="preserve"> 
  <div> 
   <p begin="00:00:02.586" end="00:00:04.547" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マオ）アローラ！　マオだよー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:05.047" end="00:00:08.008" style="s1"><span style="s2">今回の“ポケもんだい”は<br />あたしが出すからね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:08.509" end="00:00:09.552" style="s3"><span style="s2">今日のお話で<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:09.677" end="00:00:13.055" style="s3"><span style="s2">アーカラじまへ行くのに使う乗り物<br />なーんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:13.180" end="00:00:15.266" style="s3"><span style="s2">答えは番組の後半！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:17.226" end="00:00:18.185" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピッ ピッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:18.310" end="00:00:21.647" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）アーカラアーカラアーカラ<br />アーカラアーカラアーカラアーカラじま～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:21.772" end="00:00:23.107" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロトム）サトシー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:23.232" end="00:00:26.068" style="s1"><span style="s2">今日から課外授業だからって<br />浮かれすぎロト～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:26.736" end="00:00:27.945" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ああ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:28.070" end="00:00:32.324" style="s1"><span style="s2">ロトム アーカラじまで会えるポケモンって<br />どんなのがいるんだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:32.616" end="00:00:35.369" style="s1"><span style="s2">待つロト　検索するロト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:36.537" end="00:00:37.204" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:37.329" end="00:00:39.331" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ケンタロス）モー！<br />（サトシ）うわあ～！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:39.623" end="00:00:40.666" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ケンタロス）モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:40.958" end="00:00:42.668" style="s1"><span style="s2">モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:43.586" end="00:00:44.795" style="s1"><span style="s2">モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:44.920" end="00:00:46.922" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒）落ち着け ケンタロス！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:47.339" end="00:00:49.550" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）リザードン<br />そのまま押さえてるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:49.675" end="00:00:51.761" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リザードン）グォ…<br />（ケンタロス）モー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:51.886" end="00:00:52.553" style="s1"><span style="s2">（落下音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:53.179" end="00:00:55.181" style="s1"><span style="s2">ええ… ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:55.306" end="00:00:56.599" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リーリエ）大丈夫ですか？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:56.724" end="00:00:58.434" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）って どうかな…<br />（ロトム）ピピピ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:00:58.559" end="00:01:01.061" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ケンタロス）モー<br />（サトシ）どうしたんだ アレ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:01.479" end="00:01:04.690" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マーマネ）リザードンの着陸に<br />ケンタロスが驚いちゃってね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:05.024" end="00:01:07.234" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）興奮して 怒った…<br />（ケンタロス）モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:09.153" end="00:01:09.820" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リザードン）グォ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:12.072" end="00:01:12.782" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒）うわっ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:16.035" end="00:01:16.994" style="s1"><span style="s2">ルガルガンだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:17.119" end="00:01:18.370" style="s1"><span style="s2">真昼の姿ロト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:18.496" end="00:01:22.708" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ケンタロス）モー！　モーモ！　モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:23.000" end="00:01:24.084" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）アローラ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:24.543" end="00:01:25.753" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）うん？<br />（ピカチュウ）ピカ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:26.128" end="00:01:28.005" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）そんなに怒らないの</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:28.506" end="00:01:31.258" style="s1"><span style="s2">よーしよーし いい子ね～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:31.383" end="00:01:32.176" style="s1"><span style="s2">（キスの音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:32.301" end="00:01:34.386" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）えー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:34.845" end="00:01:36.847" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）よーし よしよし<br />（ケンタロス）モー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:37.515" end="00:01:38.557" style="s1"><span style="s2">スゲー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:38.849" end="00:01:40.059" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピーカー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:40.267" end="00:01:41.560" style="s1"><span style="s2">カッコいい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:41.685" end="00:01:42.895" style="s1"><span style="s2">誰だろう？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:43.020" end="00:01:45.564" style="s1"><span style="s2">スクールの人じゃないみたいだけど</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:46.482" end="00:01:49.777" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ナレーター）<span style="s5">暴れるケンタロスを</span><br /><span style="s5">落ち着かせたルガルガンと―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:49.902" end="00:01:52.363" style="s3"><span style="s2">この女性は一体？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:01:56.075" end="00:01:58.077" region="縦右">♪～</p> 
   <p begin="00:03:18.782" end="00:03:20.784" region="縦右">～♪</p> 
   <p begin="00:03:31.086" end="00:03:36.091" style="s1"><span style="s2">リザードンも よく押さえてくれたじゃない<br />さすがの貫禄ね フフッ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:36.216" end="00:03:37.343" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）ライチさん！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:37.551" end="00:03:40.429" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）アローラ カキ！　ウハハ<br />（カキ）うぉ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:40.804" end="00:03:44.141" style="s1"><span style="s2">ちょっと見ない間に<br />たくましくなっちゃって</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:44.975" end="00:03:46.435" style="s1"><span style="s2">カッコいいじゃない</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:46.977" end="00:03:48.812" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）カキ 知り合い？<br />（カキ）ああ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:49.396" end="00:03:52.316" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）アーカラじまの しまクイーン<br />ライチさんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:52.650" end="00:03:54.860" style="s1"><span style="s2">ええ！　しまクイーン！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:58.197" end="00:03:59.031" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ククイ博士）というわけで…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:03:59.657" end="00:04:03.911" style="s1"><span style="s2">このクラスは今日からアーカラじまへの<br />課外授業に出かけるわけだが…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:04.078" end="00:04:06.288" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハイハーイ 行きます！　大試練！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:06.413" end="00:04:10.542" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ククイ博士）サトシ　気が早いぞ<br />（サトシ）だってさー ハハハ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:10.668" end="00:04:13.921" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マオ）サトシー<br />（マーマネ）サトシったらさ～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:14.338" end="00:04:17.967" style="s1"><span style="s2">アローラ！<br />アーカラじまのしまクイーン ライチよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:18.717" end="00:04:21.971" style="s1"><span style="s2">今回の課外授業は<br />あたしが仕切るから よろしくね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:22.596" end="00:04:24.515" style="s1"><span style="s2">じゃあ まずは<span style="s6"><span style="s7">挨拶</span><span style="s8">あいさつ</span></span>がわりに…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:24.890" end="00:04:26.392" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）キャー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:26.517" end="00:04:27.559" style="s1"><span style="s2">（倒れる音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:28.644" end="00:04:29.853" style="s1"><span style="s2">（一同）う…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:30.020" end="00:04:33.190" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハハハ…　気にしない 気にしな～い</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:33.941" end="00:04:34.900" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）はーい これ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:35.651" end="00:04:37.236" style="s1"><span style="s2">さっすがライチさん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:37.528" end="00:04:38.612" style="s1"><span style="s2">ステキです</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:38.737" end="00:04:39.989" style="s1"><span style="s2">（アママイコ）アマーイ<br />（マオ）きれ～い</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:40.614" end="00:04:43.409" style="s1"><span style="s2">うん　海の中みたい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:43.826" end="00:04:46.036" style="s1"><span style="s2">これ なんていう鉱石かな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:46.787" end="00:04:49.665" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ん～　ピカチュウ どうだ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:50.040" end="00:04:50.749" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:51.333" end="00:04:52.418" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカチュウ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:52.584" end="00:04:56.755" style="s1"><span style="s2">そりゃ アクセサリーもらっても<br />男の子にはビミョーよね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:57.006" end="00:04:59.550" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）え… ええ…<br />そんなことないですよ ライチさん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:04:59.675" end="00:05:02.678" style="s1"><span style="s2">本当？　実はね 私 ほら</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:03.178" end="00:05:05.389" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）手作りのショップもやってるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:05.973" end="00:05:07.099" style="s1"><span style="s2"><span style="s6"><span style="s7">Ｚ</span><span style="s8">ゼット</span></span>リング</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:07.224" end="00:05:10.102" style="s1"><span style="s2">ここに ついているのは<br />いわのＺクリスタル</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:10.352" end="00:05:12.730" style="s1"><span style="s2">いわタイプか　いいな～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:12.855" end="00:05:14.940" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）キミは島めぐりしているのかな？<br />（ピカチュウ）ピ？　ピーカー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:15.065" end="00:05:17.985" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハイ　ライチさんの大試練も受けたいです！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:18.110" end="00:05:21.280" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）<br />んー それはこの課外授業次第かな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:21.572" end="00:05:23.574" style="s1"><span style="s2">よっしゃ 燃えてきた！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:23.824" end="00:05:27.077" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピ ピーカー　ピカ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:27.453" end="00:05:28.162" style="s1"><span style="s2">ウフ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:28.787" end="00:05:33.709" style="s1"><span style="s2">さあ！　ポケモンを連れて 荷物を持って<br />アーカラじまへ レッツ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:34.585" end="00:05:36.462" style="s1"><span style="s2">（オーキド校長）ゴー…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:36.587" end="00:05:39.423" style="s1"><span style="s2">アローラ 校長先生　お久しぶり</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:39.548" end="00:05:42.676" style="s1"><span style="s2">せっかく来たんだから<br />生徒たちのポケモンたちを<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:42.801" end="00:05:46.180" style="s1"><span style="s2">まずは予習したらどうかナットレイ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:46.972" end="00:05:52.770" style="s1"><span style="s2">どうかナットレイ？　アハ<br />何それ 最高！　アハハハ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:52.895" end="00:05:54.813" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒たち）うわぁ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:56.065" end="00:05:58.400" style="s1"><span style="s2">ワーオ！　ワオワオすごーい！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:05:58.901" end="00:06:02.613" style="s1"><span style="s2">どの子も いい顔～<br />愛情いっぱいもらってるんだね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:02.821" end="00:06:06.867" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ポケモンたちの鳴き声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:07.117" end="00:06:08.285" style="s1"><span style="s2">（モクローの鳴き声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:08.410" end="00:06:10.871" style="s1"><span style="s2">はあ　お日様の匂い</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:10.996" end="00:06:14.333" style="s1"><span style="s2">でしょ！<br />俺もなんか分かんないけど嗅いじゃう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:14.458" end="00:06:17.544" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロトム）不思議ロト<br />みんな全然警戒してないロト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:17.669" end="00:06:18.378" style="s1"><span style="s2">（シャッター音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:18.545" end="00:06:19.254" style="s1"><span style="s2">ですね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:19.671" end="00:06:22.049" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リーリエ）それどころか<br />とっても うれしそうです</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:22.341" end="00:06:24.718" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）なんだか<br />ライチさんもポケモンみたい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:24.843" end="00:06:25.511" style="s1"><span style="s2">ん？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:26.136" end="00:06:27.930" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）あれ？　ニャビー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:28.097" end="00:06:28.889" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:30.974" end="00:06:31.642" style="s1"><span style="s2">おいで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:33.685" end="00:06:36.355" style="s1"><span style="s2">ああ ライチさん<br />こいつ慣れてない人だと…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:36.480" end="00:06:38.899" style="s1"><span style="s2">大丈夫　おいで</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:43.278" end="00:06:44.613" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:45.239" end="00:06:47.491" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）んー　んふふ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:47.991" end="00:06:49.118" style="s1"><span style="s2">仲良くしてね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:49.243" end="00:06:50.077" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャーオ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:50.536" end="00:06:52.079" style="s1"><span style="s2">あらま デレデレ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:52.371" end="00:06:54.498" style="s1"><span style="s2">さっすがしまクイーンって感じ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:54.623" end="00:06:58.710" style="s1"><span style="s2">いや しまクイーンの中でも<br />ライチさんは特別だろうな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:06:59.253" end="00:07:01.672" style="s1"><span style="s2">大試練に挑んだ時は 驚いたぜ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:02.589" end="00:07:03.465" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）<span style="s5">それまで―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:03.590" end="00:07:07.761" style="s3"><span style="s2">バクガメスが初対面の人に<br />気を許すことなんて なかったからな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:08.220" end="00:07:12.933" style="s3"><span style="s2">きっとライチさんには<br />ポケモンの心を開かせる何かがあるんだろう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:14.768" end="00:07:16.478" style="s1"><span style="s2">（イワンコの鳴き声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:17.229" end="00:07:20.149" style="s1"><span style="s2">イワンコもこんなふうに<br />カッコよくなりたいよな〜</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:20.274" end="00:07:21.150" style="s1"><span style="s2">アン！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:21.692" end="00:07:24.820" style="s1"><span style="s2">ルガルガン<br />かわいい後輩ができて よかったね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:24.945" end="00:07:25.612" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ルガルガン）ワン！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:27.698" end="00:07:31.493" style="s1"><span style="s2">ん～ ほ～んとかわいい　アハハ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:31.702" end="00:07:34.997" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）アハ ねえ<br />この子たちのこともっと教えて</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:35.122" end="00:07:37.082" style="s1"><span style="s2">みんなと仲良くなりたいから</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:37.332" end="00:07:39.751" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）それじゃあ イワンコから<br />（イワンコ）アンアン！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:40.752" end="00:07:42.045" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ネッコアラの寝息）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:45.883" end="00:07:48.135" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ネッコアラの寝息）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:48.844" end="00:07:52.764" style="s1"><span style="s2">イイ… ゲットまでにいろいろあったのね…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:52.890" end="00:07:56.143" style="s1"><span style="s2">ニャビー…<br />サトシんとこ来てよかったね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:56.268" end="00:07:57.394" style="s1"><span style="s2">エヘヘ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:07:57.561" end="00:08:00.147" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リーリエ）ライチさん よかったら<br />（ライチ）あ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:00.564" end="00:08:02.900" style="s1"><span style="s2">あらま ありがと</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:03.233" end="00:08:05.652" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチのすすり泣き）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:05.777" end="00:08:06.737" style="s1"><span style="s2">（鼻をかむ音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:06.862" end="00:08:07.529" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リーリエ）え…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:07.905" end="00:08:11.909" style="s1"><span style="s2">忙しい人　笑って泣いて鼻かんで…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:13.035" end="00:08:17.748" style="s1"><span style="s2">みんなのポケモンたちは 幸せものだね<br />パートナーに恵まれて</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:18.540" end="00:08:22.127" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）今話してくれたこと<br />その気持ち 忘れずにね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:22.544" end="00:08:24.379" style="s1"><span style="s2">きっと一生の宝物になるから</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:24.504" end="00:08:25.756" style="s1"><span style="s2">（シロン）コーン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:28.550" end="00:08:33.472" style="s1"><span style="s2">キミも大試練に桃戦してきた頃より<br />ずいぶんたくましくなったね～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:33.847" end="00:08:35.432" style="s1"><span style="s2">カキに似てきたんじゃな～い？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:35.557" end="00:08:37.017" style="s1"><span style="s2">（バクガメス）ガメガ…<br />（ライチ）アハハハ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:37.142" end="00:08:38.894" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）いや どうかな…<br />（ライチ）くすぐったいって</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:40.062" end="00:08:43.482" style="s1"><span style="s2">よーし ポケモンたちの話を<br />聞かせてくれたお礼に…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:44.399" end="00:08:46.860" style="s1"><span style="s2">アーカラじまのこと 話しちゃお！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:48.237" end="00:08:50.572" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロトム）ピピピ　記録開始ロト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:51.198" end="00:08:55.535" style="s1"><span style="s2">アーカラじまは<br />ヴェラ火山の神聖な炎に育まれた<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:08:55.661" end="00:08:58.956" style="s1"><span style="s2">人々に感謝と恐れを抱かせる島</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:00.374" end="00:09:04.544" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）で そのアーカラじまの守り神と<br />言われているポケモンのこと<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:04.670" end="00:09:05.629" style="s1"><span style="s2">みんな知ってる？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:06.296" end="00:09:07.464" style="s1"><span style="s2">カプ･テテフ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:07.714" end="00:09:08.382" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピーカー？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:08.757" end="00:09:11.802" style="s1"><span style="s2">おお！　いいね～ 知ってるね～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:26.483" end="00:09:27.943" region="縦右">（サトシ）<br /><span style="s5">キミに決めた！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:28.151" end="00:09:30.279" region="縦右">（ケンタロス）<br /><span style="s5">モー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:37.953" end="00:09:40.998" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）<span style="s5">アーカラじまの守り神</span><br /><span style="s5">カプ･テテフは―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:41.123" end="00:09:43.333" style="s3"><span style="s2">光る<span style="s6"><span style="s7">鱗粉</span><span style="s8">りんぷん</span></span>をふりまくことがあるの</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:44.167" end="00:09:49.089" style="s3"><span style="s2">その鱗粉に触れた者は<br />たちまち元気を取り戻すと言われてるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:49.464" end="00:09:51.717" style="s1"><span style="s2">そっか だからあの時…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:52.426" end="00:09:53.218" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カプ･テテフ）テテ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:09:56.013" end="00:09:56.763" style="s1"><span style="s2">あ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:00.350" end="00:10:02.144" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）あたしは こう考えてる</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:02.436" end="00:10:04.646" style="s1"><span style="s2">カプ･テテフは命の神</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:05.063" end="00:10:09.443" style="s1"><span style="s2">その光は傷をも癒やし<br />命に力を与えてくれる</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:10.402" end="00:10:12.237" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）また 会えるかな</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:12.362" end="00:10:15.949" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）もちろん<br />キミが会いたいって思っていたらね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:16.616" end="00:10:20.287" style="s1"><span style="s2">みんながこの課外授業で<br />カプ･テテフの息吹に触れて<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:20.620" end="00:10:23.498" style="s1"><span style="s2">命ってなんなのか<br />考えてくれたらうれしい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:23.665" end="00:10:28.295" style="s1"><span style="s2">そして あたしたちとポケモン<br />命と命が出会うことで<span style="s4">―</span></span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:28.420" end="00:10:32.549" style="s1"><span style="s2">そのパートナー同士にだけ生まれる何かを<br />感じてほしい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:32.966" end="00:10:35.093" style="s1"><span style="s2">ちょっと難しいかもしれないけどね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:36.178" end="00:10:37.387" style="s1"><span style="s2">ウフフッフ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:38.597" end="00:10:40.474" style="s1"><span style="s2">じゃあ 話は終わり</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:40.766" end="00:10:46.063" style="s1"><span style="s2">今度こそ ポケモン連れて 荷物持って<br />アーカラじまへ レッツゴー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:48.231" end="00:10:49.691" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒たち）おお！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:50.108" end="00:10:52.486" style="s1"><span style="s2">ハーイ みんな乗って乗って！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:53.945" end="00:10:54.780" style="s1"><span style="s2">ウア！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:54.905" end="00:10:55.906" style="s1"><span style="s2">（倒れる音）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:56.323" end="00:10:57.491" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒たち）ああ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:10:58.658" end="00:11:00.744" style="s1"><span style="s2">大丈夫 大丈夫…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:01.286" end="00:11:02.204" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:02.371" end="00:11:03.538" style="s1"><span style="s2">アハハハ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:03.663" end="00:11:07.667" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）忙しい人<br />真面目に語って笑って こけて…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:08.001" end="00:11:09.669" style="s1"><span style="s2">うん！　カッコいい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:09.836" end="00:11:10.670" style="s1"><span style="s2">どこが？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:14.174" end="00:11:15.509" style="s1"><span style="s2">いってきまーす</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:15.926" end="00:11:18.637" style="s1"><span style="s2">元気でいってコイキングー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:26.520" end="00:11:28.814" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ああー！　気持ちいい！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:28.939" end="00:11:30.148" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ピカチュウ）ピーカー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:30.607" end="00:11:32.818" style="s1"><span style="s2">海から行くのもいいな リザードン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:32.943" end="00:11:33.610" style="s1"><span style="s2">ガァオ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:34.027" end="00:11:35.904" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ！　 カキが映ってる</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:36.029" end="00:11:36.696" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マオ･サトシ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:37.197" end="00:11:38.407" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ホントだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:38.532" end="00:11:40.742" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マーマネ）アーカラじまの観光ガイドだよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:40.867" end="00:11:42.911" style="s1"><span style="s2">カキんちが紹介されてるんだ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:43.036" end="00:11:45.997" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マオ）何 この顔！　緊張しすぎでしょ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:46.123" end="00:11:47.749" style="s1"><span style="s2">いーだろ 別に！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:53.171" end="00:11:54.798" style="s1"><span style="s2">リラックスしてますね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:55.173" end="00:11:55.882" style="s1"><span style="s2">うん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:11:56.550" end="00:12:00.262" style="s1"><span style="s2">アーカラじま<br />どんな水ポケモンがいるか 楽しみ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:00.512" end="00:12:05.851" style="s1"><span style="s2">食べ物も楽しみだな～<br />きっとレアな食材もいっぱいあるから</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:07.686" end="00:12:09.271" style="s1"><span style="s2">あっ なんか跳ねた</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:09.396" end="00:12:10.439" style="s1"><span style="s2">（リーリエ･マオ）え？<br />（アシマリ）アウ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:10.689" end="00:12:12.399" style="s1"><span style="s2">どこどこ？　見たい！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:12.732" end="00:12:15.318" style="s1"><span style="s2">うーん？　いないけど…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:15.444" end="00:12:17.154" style="s1"><span style="s2">僕も捕捉できないロト</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:20.574" end="00:12:22.200" style="s1"><span style="s2">何か 見つけたみたい</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:22.576" end="00:12:25.078" style="s1"><span style="s2">了解！　寄り道 行っちゃおう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:25.579" end="00:12:27.038" style="s1"><span style="s2">とりかーじ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:29.082" end="00:12:29.833" style="s1"><span style="s2">（マーマネ･サトシ）え？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:29.958" end="00:12:31.793" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）興味を持ったら 行かなきゃね！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:32.210" end="00:12:35.130" style="s1"><span style="s2">アハ　ライチさん分かってる～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:46.308" end="00:12:47.142" style="s1"><span style="s2">出たー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:50.562" end="00:12:53.064" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ロトム）ハクリューロト！<br />（生徒たち）おお！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:12:56.193" end="00:12:59.779" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒たちの驚く声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:02.365" end="00:13:03.617" style="s1"><span style="s2">（雷鳴）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:04.284" end="00:13:04.993" style="s1"><span style="s2">うわ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:05.118" end="00:13:06.536" style="s1"><span style="s2">ワーオ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:06.828" end="00:13:09.039" style="s1"><span style="s2">これ ハクリューがやったの？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:09.372" end="00:13:11.791" style="s1"><span style="s2">課外授業は もう始まってるよ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:12.083" end="00:13:14.586" style="s1"><span style="s2">海のポケモンたちに 触れ合っていこう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:20.884" end="00:13:24.137" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ヤドン）ヤドン ヤドン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:24.262" end="00:13:28.558" style="s1"><span style="s2">（キャモメの鳴き声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:36.233" end="00:13:36.942" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）ケイコウオ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:37.526" end="00:13:38.193" style="s1"><span style="s2">メノクラゲ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:38.777" end="00:13:39.444" style="s1"><span style="s2">ネオラント</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:40.028" end="00:13:40.695" style="s1"><span style="s2">ラブカス</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:41.071" end="00:13:42.113" style="s1"><span style="s2">サニーゴ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:42.322" end="00:13:43.406" style="s1"><span style="s2">シェルダー</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:43.615" end="00:13:44.991" style="s1"><span style="s2">あ ルギアも</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:45.116" end="00:13:45.825" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ･マーマネ･サトシ）え！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:45.951" end="00:13:47.661" style="s1"><span style="s2">どこどこどこ ルギア！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:47.911" end="00:13:50.497" style="s1"><span style="s2">もう 男子信じてるし</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:50.622" end="00:13:52.541" style="s1"><span style="s2">んなわけないでしょ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:52.707" end="00:13:53.625" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）でした</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:53.750" end="00:13:54.543" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ･マーマネ･カキ）だは…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:54.793" end="00:13:55.794" style="s1"><span style="s2">アウアウ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:56.461" end="00:13:58.421" style="s1"><span style="s2">水ポケモン 詳しいのね</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:58.630" end="00:13:59.548" style="s1"><span style="s2">あ…</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:13:59.798" end="00:14:00.674" style="s1"><span style="s2">大好き！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:00.799" end="00:14:01.633" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）う～ん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:02.884" end="00:14:04.427" style="s1"><span style="s2">もっと何か いないかな～</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:05.345" end="00:14:06.179" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）ヒャー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:06.972" end="00:14:08.557" style="s1"><span style="s2">（スイレン）大変！<br />（サトシ）ライチさん！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:09.724" end="00:14:11.935" style="s1"><span style="s2">ウハッ 最高！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:12.143" end="00:14:13.853" style="s1"><span style="s2">（生徒たち）ああ…<br />（ライチ）みんなもおいでよ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:13.979" end="00:14:15.188" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）すっごいキレイ！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:15.855" end="00:14:17.524" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ピカチュウ 行くか！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:17.649" end="00:14:18.692" style="s1"><span style="s2">ピカー！</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:41.047" end="00:14:42.465" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）お？<br />（ライチ）ん？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:45.844" end="00:14:46.511" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ライチ）んん</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:47.220" end="00:14:48.263" style="s1"><span style="s2">（サトシ）ぷは<br />（ピカチュウ）ピーカ</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:48.555" end="00:14:49.514" style="s1"><span style="s2">なんだろ？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:49.639" end="00:14:50.599" style="s1"><span style="s2">行ってみよう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:53.101" end="00:14:54.144" style="s1"><span style="s2">（イワンコ）ワン ワンワンワン</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:54.269" end="00:14:55.228" style="s1"><span style="s2">（カキ）おあ…<br />（ククイ博士）ん？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:55.604" end="00:14:57.981" style="s1"><span style="s2">（イワンコ）ワン<br />（カキ）どうしたんだ サトシたち？</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:14:58.273" end="00:15:00.442" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ククイ博士）気になるな　追いかけよう</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:15:08.658" end="00:15:11.244" style="s1"><span style="s2">（ホエルコの鳴き声）</span></p> 
   <p begin="00:15:11.703" end="00:15:12.787" style="s1"><span style="s2">ホエルコだ</span></p> 
